          "component_id": "talent",
          "data": {
            "list": [
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">普通攻击</span></p><p>造成2点<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">物理伤害</span>。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2023/12/20/157749474/47817b4476bcd8b44c86c87debf042f2_5094479183797041794.png",
                "id": "talent83351",
                "key": "裂爪横击",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 1,
                    "point_type": "anemo"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "black"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "裂爪横击"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">元素战技</span></p><p>造成2点<span style=\"color: #80FFD7\">风元素伤害</span>，目标角色附属<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">坍毁</span>。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2023/12/20/157749474/bb0d49f020ec5da8ac945ca46a5f763f_6368520211290730735.png",
                "id": "talent37094",
                "key": "暴风轰击",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "anemo"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "暴风轰击"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">元素战技</span></p><p>造成2点<span style=\"color: #80FFD7\">风元素伤害</span>，然后分别准备技能：<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">长延涤流</span>和<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">终幕涤流</span>。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2023/12/20/157749474/6d9f17ac20b8806cbca36313e77bdf23_3735635038661776524.png",
                "id": "talent74",
                "key": "风龙涤流",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 5,
                    "point_type": "anemo"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "风龙涤流"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">元素爆发</span></p><p>造成5点<span style=\"color: #80FFD7\">风元素伤害</span>，所有敌方后台角色附属<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">坍毁</span>。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2023/12/20/157749474/fdffcf6a8e033feb0d73ad38a747e0e4_6012742993362977465.png",
                "id": "talent8617",
                "key": "终天闭幕曲",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 4,
                    "point_type": "anemo"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "recharge"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "终天闭幕曲"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p>和已附着的元素发生元素反应：</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 255, 215)\">风元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">冰元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">扩散（冰）</span>：对目标以外的所有敌方角色造成1点冰伤害</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 255, 215)\">风元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">水元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">扩散（水）</span>：对目标以外的所有敌方角色造成1点水伤害</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 255, 215)\">风元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">火元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">扩散（火）</span>：对目标以外的所有敌方角色造成1点火伤害</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 255, 215)\">风元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">雷元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">扩散（雷）</span>：对目标以外的所有敌方角色造成1点雷伤害</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2023/12/20/157749474/c97292d96456bfe4abeca16bfce801e4_5302994025434969197.png",
                "id": "talent9619",
                "key": "风元素伤害",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "风元素伤害"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">物理伤害</span></strong></p><p>物理伤害不会附着元素，也不会发生元素反应。</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">可用次数</span></strong></p><p>此牌效果触发后，会消耗1次<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">可用次数</span>；</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">可用次数</span>耗尽后，立刻弃置此牌。</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">坍毁</span></strong></p><p>所附属角色受到的<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">物理伤害</span>或<span style=\"color: #80FFD7\">风元素伤害</span>+2。</p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">可用次数：1</span></p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">长延涤流</span></strong></p><p>（需准备1个行动轮）</p><p>对下一个敌方后台角色造成1点<span style=\"color: #80FFD7\">风元素伤害</span>，然后准备技能：<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">终幕涤流</span>。（敌方没有后台角色时，改为对出战角色造成伤害）</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">终幕涤流</span></strong></p><p>（需准备1个行动轮）</p><p>对上一个敌方后台角色造成2点<span style=\"color: #80FFD7\">风元素伤害</span>。（敌方没有后台角色时，改为对出战角色造成伤害）</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2023/12/20/157749474/07bae546ac7c69ef6402170b283840c5_888772437509516990.png",
